INSERT INTO tee_dcap_collateral
            (kind, sha256, not_after, updated, update_guard_expires)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, transaction_timestamp(), NULL)
            ON CONFLICT (kind)
            DO UPDATE SET
            sha256 = $2,
            not_after = $3,
            updated = transaction_timestamp(),
            update_guard_expires = NULL
